--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Scenario number : 1
Use case        : shipping companies management
Scenario name   : add shipping company
Description     :

1. Connect through a web browser to Bazaar system.
2. Select the "Login" link.
3. Login as administrator.
4. Select the link "Compagnie Postali" and then "Aggiungi".
4. Insert values and press the button "Conferma".

Expected results:

1. The new shipping company is added to the system.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Scenario number : 2
Use case        : shipping companies management
Scenario name   : modify shipping company
Description     :

1. Connect through a web browser to Bazaar system.
2. Select the "Login" link.
3. Login as administrator.
4. Insert a shipping company as in scenario 1.
5. Select the link "Modifica" in the countries list page, for the company
   just inserted.
6. Change the values and press the button "Conferma".

Expected results:

1. The company is correctly changed.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Scenario number : 3
Use case        : shipping companies management
Scenario name   : delete shipping company
Description     :

1. Connect through a web browser to Bazaar system.
2. Select the "Login" link.
3. Login as administrator.
4. Insert a company as in scenario 1.
5. Select the link "Cancella" and confirm the deletion.

Expected results:

1. The company is correctly deleted.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Scenario number : 4
Use case        : shipping companies management
Scenario name   : paging
Description     :

1. Connect through a web browser to Bazaar system.
2. Select the "Login" link.
3. Login as administrator.
4. Insert 25 companies repeating 25 times scenario 1.
5. Verify the paging adding, removing end changing the companies.

Expected results:

1. The companies paging works fine.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Scenario number : 5
Use case        : shipping companies management
Scenario name   : unauthorized access
Description     :

1. Connect through a web browser to Bazaar system.
2. Insert the following url in the browser address txt box:
		http://<host>:<port>/<context>/adminListShipping.do
		http://<host>:<port>/<context>/adminAddShipping.do
		http://<host>:<port>/<context>/adminEditShipping.do

Expected results:

1. The following message is displayed:
	"Autorizzazione non consentita. L'operazione richiesta necessita delle 
	credenziali di amministratore."
